'''''Siol''''' was a [[Ferryboat liner]] that carried smugglers from ''[[Dunari's Rest]]'' when the station was attacked by Imperial forces. It made it to hyperspace intact thanks to assistance from the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]].

